{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_bdrk_0146KD72dWW3gFKMzVBRTm8M","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good, I'm on the correct branch. Now let me implement US-017: **Implement publisher facet section**.\n\nLooking at the requirements:\n- Publisher FacetSection renders only when mediaType=video_game or on mixed-content pages where at least one publisher value exists\n- NOT rendered on movies, TV, books, or audiobooks single-type pages\n- Section header reads 'Publisher'\n- Uses FacetCheckboxList and ExpandableList (up to 15, Show more/less)\n- Multiple publishers can be selected (OR logic)\n- Selecting a publisher updates URL param publishers as comma-separated values and resets page to 1\n- All user-facing strings wrapped with @lingui/macro t or <Trans>\n\nLet me create the PublisherSection component:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":176,"cache_read_input_tokens":77067,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":176,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"763b6f1c-fd72-45a9-b674-0ced32a3b50e","uuid":"93e799ea-a1bd-4859-a8c1-e70d7528df1b"}
